node.text:
The 1992 Summer Olympics in Barcelona saw a transformation in the cityscape which would turn the Catalan city into a skateboarder’s paradise and to this day remains a Mecca for skaters who want to add their chapter to the city’s skateboarding lore.

Episode 4 of #MundoGustavo touches down in the world’s greatest skateboarding city as @gustavoribeiro and his brother join an @ementasb filming mission.

Watch the full episode now. Link in bio. 🔑 
#skate #skateboarding #skatelife #barcelona
